    "name": "Via Hotel Taipei Station",
    "detail": "This hotel is better than expected with its location. I stay in deluxe room that will have window and believed the standard room will not have the window. This is norm for hotel in Taipei and most of it also equipped with small room. The hotel is opposite Citibank and next to a Japanese restaurant and Family mart. Behind the hotel is the Chinese Temple @ 城隍廟 and opposite it there is vegetarian restaurant. Along the way to Taipei station (opposite City Inn I) I found also have 3 vegetarian restaurants. This is extremely good news for those want to stay somewhere in this area or this hotel. The hotel provide 24hrs free soft drink (incl apple juice), snack and hot coffee/chocolate drink. For breakfast, they provide toast/break. The hotel is near to 3 MRT stations (Taipei, XiMenDing & NTU Hospital). This hotel also provide massage tool for those that need it after the shopping. Will come back to this hotel again.",
